videos.description: Texas A &M's Christian Kirk lets the ball slip through his arms for the first turnover of the game.
videos.headline: South Carolina recovers muffed punt

videos.description: Trayveon Williams takes it in from one-yard out for the first score of the game.
videos.headline: Williams gets the Aggies on the board

videos.description: Jake Bentley escapes two defenders and throws a 45 yard strike to Shi Smith to even the score.
videos.headline: South Carolina pulls a Houdini on TD pass

videos.description: South Carolina head coach Will Muschamp sheds some light on how the Gamecocks can improve in the second half.
videos.headline: Muschamp on South Carolina's man down man up mentality

videos.description: Jake Bentley finds OrTre Smith for the 13-yard touchdown pass in the third quarter.
videos.headline: Bentley connects with Smith for 2nd TD of the night

videos.description: Cameron Buckley is ejected for targeting in the fourth quarter costing the Aggies six.
videos.headline: Targeting penalty takes Texas A&M TD off the board

videos.description: Keith Ford ties the game with a seven yard touchdown in the fourth quarter.
videos.headline: Ford pushes the pile all the way for TD

videos.description: Keith Ford scores his second rushing touchdown of the night on a 17-yard run to give the Aggies the lead.
videos.headline: Ford gets 2nd rushing TD

videos.description: Keith Ford talks about what his style of play brings to the Aggies' offense.
videos.headline: Ford on his 2-TD performance

videos.headline: Texas A&M's sensational defense carries Aggies to victory
